  ANIMALS OF THE WORLD
============================================================

Name:         African Wild Dog
Scientific:   Lycaon pictus
Class:        Mammalia
Habitat:      Savanna
Diet:         Carnivore
Lifespan:     11 years
Weight:       30 kg
Status:       Endangered
Fact:         80% hunting success rate; votes on hunts by sneezing democratically

Name:         Axolotl
Scientific:   Ambystoma mexicanum
Class:        Amphibia
Habitat:      Lakes
Diet:         Carnivore
Lifespan:     15 years
Weight:       0.3 kg
Status:       Critically Endangered
Fact:         Can regenerate entire limbs, spine, heart, and brain tissue

Name:         Peregrine Falcon
Scientific:   Falco peregrinus
Class:        Aves
Habitat:      Cliffs/Cities
Diet:         Carnivore
Lifespan:     15 years
Weight:       1 kg
Status:       Least Concern
Fact:         Fastest animal on Earth at 389 km/h in a dive

